{"type":"assistant","uuid":"20260312045651c5061281e45d4eb9","session_id":"9310a036-0fcf-4395-9365-74ce968ab0f4","message":{"id":"20260312045651c5061281e45d4eb9","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"call_e526d175d46e4e4abc84516d","name":"Write","input":{"content":"# F-007: Test and Validation Suite\n\n## Summary\n\n建立 Telegram 管道能力的测试体系，覆盖命令路由、计划文件接入、进程控制、状态聚合与权限校验。使用 Node.js 内置 test runner，补充单元与集成测试，确保核心流程在改动后可回归验证。\n\n**Dependencies**: F-003 (Plan Ingestion), F-004 (Pipeline Controller), F-005 (Status & Logs), F-006 (Safety Guard) — all completed\n\n---\n\n## User Stories\n\n### US-1: Command Parsing & Routing Tests\n\n**As a** 开发者 **I want** 命令解析与路由层有完整单元测试 **So that** 命令格式变化时可快速验证正确性\n\n**Acceptance Criteria:**\n- AC-1.1: 覆盖命令解析器 (parser) 所有分支：正常命令、空参数、非法格式\n- AC-1.2: 覆盖命令注册表 (registry) 查找与错误路径\n- AC-1.3: 覆盖参数校验器 (validator) 边界条件\n- AC-1.4: 覆盖响应格式化器 (formatter) 各种输出场景\n\n---\n\n### US-2: Control Layer Return Tests\n\n**As a** 开发者 **I want** 控制层 API 有完整测试覆盖 **So that** 返回结构与错误码变更时可防止回归\n\n**Acceptance Criteria:**\n- AC-2.1: 覆盖 pipeline-control-service 所有方法返回结构\n- AC-2.2: 覆盖 pipeline-controller (F-004) 并发锁与状态管理\n- AC-2.3: 覆盖 plan-ingestion-service 校验与版本管理逻辑\n- AC-2.4: 所有错误路径有对应测试用例\n\n---\n\n### US-3: E2E Integration Test\n\n**As a** 运维人员 **I want** 有一条端到端集成测试验证主链路 **So that** 我可以确信核心流程在部署后可用\n\n**Acceptance Criteria:**\n- AC-3.1: 测试 start → status → stop 主链路（mock 外部依赖）\n- AC-3.2: 验证状态流转正确：idle → running → stopped\n- AC-3.3: 验证错误处理：重复启动、空停止等边界场景\n- AC-3.4: 测试运行时间 < 30s，可加入 pre-commit hook\n\n---\n\n### US-4: Plan File Validation Tests\n\n**As a** 开发者 **I want** 计划文件校验与版本切换有自动化测试 **So that** 上传流程变更时可防止回归\n\n**Acceptance Criteria:**\n- AC-4.1: 覆盖 JSON schema 校验：合法文件、缺失字段、类型错误\n- AC-4.2: 覆盖版本管理：上传、列表、切换、回滚\n- AC-4.3: 覆盖版本切换边界：不存在的版本、损坏的版本文件\n- AC-4.4: 测试与 pipeline 集成点：动态切换计划文件路径\n\n---\n\n### US-5: Permission & Security Negative Tests\n\n**As a** 安全审计员 **I want** 权限与安全策略有负向测试 **So that** 未授权操作被阻断验证\n\n**Acceptance Criteria:**\n- AC-5.1: 覆盖权限分级检查：admin/operator/viewer 各级别边界\n- AC-5.2: 覆盖高风险命令拦截：stop/reset/retry/exec 权限不足场景\n- AC-5.3: 覆盖参数净化：路径穿越、shell 注入、危险字符\n- AC-5.4: 覆盖确认机制：超时取消、强制跳过 (--force)\n\n---\n\n## Non-Functional Requirements\n\n### NFR-1: Performance\n- 单元测试套件运行 < 10s\n- 集成测试套件运行 < 60s\n- 测试可并行执行\n\n### NFR-2: Coverage\n- 核心模块行覆盖率 > 80%\n- 关键路径 (happy path) 100% 覆盖\n- 错误路径 > 70% 覆盖\n\n### NFR-3: Maintainability\n- 测试文件与源文件结构对应\n- 使用统一的 mock/stub 策略\n- 测试数据集中管理\n\n---\n\n## Scope Boundaries\n\n### In Scope\n- 补充缺失的单元测试\n- 新增集成测试覆盖主链路\n- 负向测试覆盖安全策略\n- 测试工具函数与 fixtures\n- CI 集成（package.json scripts）\n\n### Out of Scope\n- 性能/压力测试\n- 端到端 UI 测试\n- 外部服务 mock（Telegram API）改为单元测试\n- 代码覆盖率报告服务集成\n\n---\n\n## Test Matrix\n\n| Area | Test Type | Priority | Target File |\n|------|-----------|----------|-------------|\n| Command Parser | Unit | High | tests/bot/commands/parser.test.js |\n| Command Registry | Unit | High | tests/bot/commands/registry.test.js |\n| Param Validator | Unit | High | tests/bot/commands/validator.test.js |\n| Response Formatter | Unit | Medium | tests/bot/commands/formatter.test.js |\n| Pipeline Controller | Unit | High | tests/services/pipeline-controller.test.js |\n| Plan Ingestion | Unit | High | tests/services/plan-ingestion-service.test.js |\n| Status Aggregator | Unit | High | tests/services/status-aggregator.test.js |\n| Permission Guard | Unit | High | tests/security/permission-guard.test.js |\n| Param Sanitizer | Unit | High | tests/security/param-sanitizer.test.js |\n| Confirmation Manager | Unit | Medium | tests/security/confirmation-manager.test.js |\n| E2E Main Chain | Integration | Critical | tests/integration/e2e-main-chain.test.js |\n| Permission Flow | Integration | High | tests/integration/security-flow.test.js |\n| Plan Version Flow | Integration | High | tests/integration/plan-version-flow.test.js |\n\n---\n\n## Decisions\n\n| ID | Date | Decision |\n|----|------|----------|\n| D1 | 2026-03-14 | 使用 Node.js 内置 test runner（与项目一致），不引入 Jest |\n| D2 | 2026-03-14 | 集成测试使用 mock 替代真实 shell 脚本执行 |\n| D3 | 2026-03-14 | 测试 fixtures 放置 tests/fixtures/ 目录 |\n| D4 | 2026-03-14 | 不新建覆盖率工具，使用 node --test 内置能力 |\n","file_path":"/Users/loneyu/SelfProjects/PrizmClaw/.prizmkit/specs/007-test-and-validation-suite/spec.md"}}],"model":"glm-5.0","role":"assistant","stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":36966,"output_tokens":1512,"cache_creation_input_tokens":null,"cache_read_input_tokens":null,"cache_creation":null,"server_tool_use":null,"service_tier":null}},"parent_tool_use_id":"019cdeaf93760837ebd601924e6d630f","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T20:57:25.425Z","_requestId":"f8b0d56a051a42089a34cee3b1b65359"}
{"type":"user","uuid":"21141524-e2fa-4632-bf57-093d3be1e5f0","session_id":"9310a036-0fcf-4395-9365-74ce968ab0f4","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"call_e526d175d46e4e4abc84516d","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully created and wrote to new file: /Users/loneyu/SelfProjects/PrizmClaw/.prizmkit/specs/007-test-and-validation-suite/spec.md"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"019cdeaf93760837ebd601924e6d630f","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T20:57:25.431Z","_requestId":"f8b0d56a051a42089a34cee3b1b65359"}
{"type":"assistant","uuid":"2026031204572520effdac3df8466d","session_id":"9310a036-0fcf-4395-9365-74ce968ab0f4","message":{"id":"2026031204572520effdac3df8466d","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now let me create the plan.md with architecture, components, interface design, data model, and testing strategy."}],"model":"glm-5.0","role":"assistant","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":null,"cache_read_input_tokens":null,"cache_creation":null,"server_tool_use":null,"service_tier":null}},"parent_tool_use_id":"019cdeaf93760837ebd601924e6d630f","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T20:58:19.866Z","_requestId":"f8b0d56a051a42089a34cee3b1b65359"}
{"type":"assistant","uuid":"2026031204572520effdac3df8466d","session_id":"9310a036-0fcf-4395-9365-74ce968ab0f4","message":{"id":"2026031204572520effdac3df8466d","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"call_b57ceb7662604bef9288aa2f","name":"Write","input":{"content":"# F-007: Test and Validation Suite — Technical Plan\n\n## Architecture Overview\n\n```\ntests/\n├── fixtures/                    # Shared test data\n│   ├── plans/                   # Sample plan files\n│   │   ├── valid-feature-list.json\n│   │   ├── valid-bug-fix-list.json\n│   │   └── invalid-*.json       # Various invalid files\n│   └── states/                  # Sample state files\n│       ├── pipeline-idle.json\n│       ├── pipeline-running.json\n│       └── pipeline-completed.json\n│\n├── unit/                        # Pure unit tests (no I/O)\n│   ├── bot/commands/\n│   ├── services/\n│   ├── security/\n│   └── pipeline-infra/\n│\n├── integration/                 # Integration tests (with I/O mock)\n│   ├── e2e-main-chain.test.js   # US-3: start → status → stop\n│   ├── plan-version-flow.test.js\n│   └── security-flow.test.js\n│\n└── helpers/                     # Test utilities\n    ├── mock-runner.js           # Mock script runner\n    ├── mock-telegram.js         # Mock Telegraf context\n    └── test-state.js            # Temporary state management\n```\n\n---\n\n## Component Design\n\n### C-1: Test Fixtures Module\n\n**Purpose**: Centralized test data management\n\n**Components**:\n- `tests/fixtures/plans/` — Sample plan files for validation tests\n- `tests/fixtures/states/` — Sample state files for pipeline tests\n- `tests/helpers/fixture-loader.js` — Lazy loading utility\n\n**Interface**:\n```typescript\n// tests/helpers/fixture-loader.js\nexport function loadFixture(relativePath: string): string;\nexport function loadJsonFixture<T>(relativePath: string): T;\nexport function getFixturePath(relativePath: string): string;\n```\n\n---\n\n### C-2: Mock Runner Module\n\n**Purpose**: Replace real shell execution with controlled responses\n\n**Interface**:\n```typescript\n// tests/helpers/mock-runner.js\nexport function createMockRunner(responses: MockResponseMap): MockRunner;\n\ninterface MockResponseMap {\n  [action: string]: MockResponse | MockResponse[];\n}\n\ninterface MockResponse {\n  ok: boolean;\n  data?: any;\n  errorCode?: string;\n  message?: string;\n  delay?: number; // Simulate execution time\n}\n```\n\n**Usage**:\n```javascript\nconst mockRunner = createMockRunner({\n  'run': { ok: true, pid: 12345, runId: 'run-001' },\n  'status': [\n    { ok: true, isRunning: true, currentFeature: 'F-001' },\n    { ok: true, isRunning: false, lastResult: 'completed' }\n  ],\n  'stop': { ok: true, previousPid: 12345 }\n});\n```\n\n---\n\n### C-3: Mock Telegram Context\n\n**Purpose**: Simulate Telegraf bot context for command handler tests\n\n**Interface**:\n```typescript\n// tests/helpers/mock-telegram.js\nexport function createMockContext(overrides?: Partial<MockContext>): MockContext;\n\ninterface MockContext {\n  message: { text?: string; document?: any; from: { id: number; username?: string } };\n  chat: { id: number };\n  reply: jest.Mock;\n  replyWithDocument: jest.Mock;\n  state: { permission?: PermissionLevel };\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### C-4: Test State Manager\n\n**Purpose**: Manage temporary state files for integration tests\n\n**Interface**:\n```typescript\n// tests/helpers/test-state.js\nexport function createTestStateDir(prefix?: string): string;\nexport function cleanupTestStateDir(path: string): void;\nexport function writeTestState(path: string, data: object): void;\nexport function readTestState<T>(path: string): T | null;\n```\n\n---\n\n## Interface Design\n\n### E2E Test Interface\n\n```typescript\n// tests/integration/e2e-main-chain.test.js\n\ndescribe('E2E: Main Chain (start → status → stop)', () => {\n  let mockRunner;\n  let controller;\n\n  beforeEach(() => {\n    mockRunner = createMockRunner(/* ... */);\n    controller = createPipelineController({ runner: mockRunner });\n  });\n\n  // Test cases...\n});\n```\n\n### Permission Test Interface\n\n```typescript\n// tests/security/permission-guard.test.js\n\ndescribe('PermissionGuard', () => {\n  describe('checkPermission', () => {\n    it('should allow admin to execute any command', () => { /* ... */ });\n    it('should block viewer from high-risk commands', () => { /* ... */ });\n    it('should respect USER_PERMISSIONS config', () => { /* ... */ });\n  });\n\n  describe('getMinPermission', () => {\n    it('should return admin for stop/reset', () => { /* ... */ });\n    it('should return operator for retry', () => { /* ... */ });\n  });\n});\n```\n\n### Plan Validation Test Interface\n\n```typescript\n// tests/services/plan-ingestion-service.test.js\n\ndescribe('PlanIngestionService', () => {\n  describe('validate', () => {\n    it('should accept valid feature-list', () => { /* ... */ });\n    it('should reject missing $schema', () => { /* ... */ });\n    it('should reject missing required fields', () => { /* ... */ });\n  });\n\n  describe('version management', () => {\n    it('should create new version on save', () => { /* ... */ });\n    it('should switch active version', () => { /* ... */ });\n    it('should rollback to previous version', () => { /* ... */ });\n  });\n});\n```\n\n---\n\n## Data Model\n\n### Test Fixture Schema\n\n```json\n// tests/fixtures/plans/valid-feature-list.json\n{\n  \"$schema\": \"dev-pipeline-feature-list-v1\",\n  \"app_name\": \"TestApp\",\n  \"features\": [\n    { \"id\": \"F-TEST-001\", \"description\": \"Test feature\", \"status\": \"pending\" }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n```json\n// tests/fixtures/states/pipeline-running.json\n{\n  \"isRunning\": true,\n  \"pid\": 12345,\n  \"currentFeature\": \"F-TEST-001\",\n  \"startedAt\": \"2026-03-14T10:00:00Z\",\n  \"completed\": [],\n  \"failed\": []\n}\n```\n\n### Mock Response Schema\n\n```json\n{\n  \"ok\": true,\n  \"runId\": \"run-001\",\n  \"pid\": 12345,\n  \"message\": \"Pipeline started\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"isRunning\": true,\n    \"currentFeature\": \"F-TEST-001\",\n    \"startedAt\": \"2026-03-14T10:00:00Z\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## Test Strategy\n\n### Layer 1: Unit Tests (Pure)\n\n**Scope**: Functions without I/O dependencies\n**Tools**: Node.js test runner + assert\n**Mock Strategy**: Function injection, no file system\n\n**Target Files**:\n- `tests/bot/commands/parser.test.js` — Command parsing logic\n- `tests/bot/commands/validator.test.js` — Parameter validation\n- `tests/security/param-sanitizer.test.js` — Sanitization rules\n- `tests/pipeline-infra/error-codes.test.js` — Error mapping\n\n### Layer 2: Unit Tests (With Mock I/O)\n\n**Scope**: Functions with file/network dependencies\n**Mock Strategy**: Mock fs, child_process, external APIs\n\n**Target Files**:\n- `tests/services/pipeline-controller.test.js` — Controller with mock runner\n- `tests/services/plan-ingestion-service.test.js` — Service with temp dirs\n- `tests/security/permission-guard.test.js` — Guard with mock config\n\n### Layer 3: Integration Tests\n\n**Scope**: Multiple components working together\n**Mock Strategy**: Mock external services, use temp file system\n\n**Target Files**:\n- `tests/integration/e2e-main-chain.test.js` — Full pipeline lifecycle\n- `tests/integration/plan-version-flow.test.js` — Plan upload → activate\n- `tests/integration/security-flow.test.js` — Permission check → confirmation\n\n---\n\n## Test Coverage Targets\n\n| Module | Current | Target | Gap |\n|--------|---------|--------|-----|\n| bot/commands/parser.js | ~70% | 90% | +20% |\n| bot/commands/validator.js | ~60% | 85% | +25% |\n| services/pipeline-controller.js | ~75% | 90% | +15% |\n| services/plan-ingestion-service.js | ~80% | 90% | +10% |\n| security/permission-guard.js | ~70% | 95% | +25% |\n| security/param-sanitizer.js | ~65% | 90% | +25% |\n| security/confirmation-manager.js | ~50% | 85% | +35% |\n\n---\n\n## Module Dependencies\n\n```\nF-007 Test Suite\n├── depends on → F-003 (plan-ingestion-service.js)\n├── depends on → F-004 (pipeline-controller.js, lock-manager.js)\n├── depends on → F-005 (status-aggregator.js, log-pager.js)\n├── depends on → F-006 (permission-guard.js, param-sanitizer.js)\n└── uses → Node.js test runner (built-in)\n```\n\n---\n\n## Risk Assessment\n\n| Risk | Probability | Impact | Mitigation |\n|------|-------------|--------|------------|\n| Existing tests have gaps | Medium | Medium | Audit current coverage, prioritize missing cases |\n| Mock strategy inconsistency | Low | Low | Create shared mock helpers |\n| Integration tests flaky | Medium | Medium | Use deterministic mocks, avoid real I/O |\n| Test data drift | Low | Medium | Version control fixtures, sync with schema |\n\n---\n\n## Testing the Tests\n\n**Self-Validation**:\n- All tests pass on clean checkout\n- Tests fail when expected (mutation testing mindset)\n- No interdependencies between test files\n- No shared mutable state\n\n**Quality Gates**:\n```bash\n# Run all tests\nnpm test\n\n# Run specific layer\nnode --test tests/unit/**/*.test.js\nnode --test tests/integration/*.test.js\n```\n\n---\n\n## Decisions\n\n| ID | Date | Decision |\n|----|------|----------|\n| P1 | 2026-03-14 | 分层测试策略：纯单元 → Mock I/O → 集成 |\n| P2 | 2026-03-14 | Mock runner 支持顺序响应模拟状态变化 |\n| P3 | 2026-03-14 | 集成测试使用临时目录，测试后清理 |\n| P4 | 2026-03-14 | Fixtures 与 schema 文件保持同步 |\n","file_path":"/Users/loneyu/SelfProjects/PrizmClaw/.prizmkit/specs/007-test-and-validation-suite/plan.md"}}],"model":"glm-5.0","role":"assistant","stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":38516,"output_tokens":2390,"cache_creation_input_tokens":null,"cache_read_input_tokens":null,"cache_creation":null,"server_tool_use":null,"service_tier":null}},"parent_tool_use_id":"019cdeaf93760837ebd601924e6d630f","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T20:58:19.872Z","_requestId":"f8b0d56a051a42089a34cee3b1b65359"}
