sts\n\n- [ ] [T-141] [P] [US-5] Enhance permission tests: admin/operator/viewer boundaries — file: tests/security/permission-guard.test.js\n- [ ] [T-142] [P] [US-5] Add high-risk command tests: stop/reset without permission — file: tests/security/permission-guard.test.js\n- [ ] [T-143] [P] [US-5] Add high-risk command tests: retry/exec permission — file: tests/security/permission-guard.test.js\n- [ ] [T-144] [P] [US-5] Enhance param sanitizer tests: path traversal — file: tests/security/param-sanitizer.test.js\n- [ ] [T-145] [P] [US-5] Enhance param sanitizer tests: shell injection — file: tests/security/param-sanitizer.test.js\n- [ ] [T-146] [P] [US-5] Enhance param sanitizer tests: dangerous chars — file: tests/security/param-sanitizer.test.js\n- [ ] [T-147] [US-5] Add confirmation manager tests: timeout cancellation — file: tests/security/confirmation-manager.test.js\n- [ ] [T-148] [US-5] Add confirmation manager tests: --force skip — file: tests/security/confirmation-manager.test.js\n- [ ] [T-149] [US-5] Add security flow integration test — file: tests/integration/security-flow.test.js\n\n---\n\n## Polish Phase (T-900+)\n\n- [ ] [T-901] Audit and document test coverage gaps — file: tests/README.md\n- [ ] [T-902] Verify all tests pass in clean environment — file: (verification)\n- [ ] [T-903] Update .prizm-docs with F-007 test infrastructure — file: .prizm-docs/runtime.prizm\n\n---\n\n## Task Details\n\n### T-001: Create test fixtures directory structure\n- **Goal**: Establish standardized fixture organization\n- **Input**: None\n- **Output**: `tests/fixtures/`, `tests/fixtures/plans/`, `tests/fixtures/states/`\n- **Acceptance**: Directories exist, .gitkeep in each\n- **Complexity**: Low\n\n### T-005: Create fixture loader helper\n- **Goal**: Provide lazy-loading utility for test fixtures\n- **Input**: Fixture relative path\n- **Output**: File content (string or parsed JSON)\n- **Acceptance**: `loadFixture()`, `loadJsonFixture()`, `getFixturePath()` exported\n- **Complexity**: Low\n\n### T-006: Create mock runner helper\n- **Goal**: Replace real shell execution with controlled responses\n- **Input**: Response map configuration\n- **Output**: Mock runner function compatible with pipeline-control-service\n- **Acceptance**: Supports action routing, response sequencing, delay simulation\n- **Complexity**: Medium\n\n### T-007: Create mock Telegram context helper\n- **Goal**: Simulate Telegraf bot context for handler tests\n- **Input**: Context overrides (message, user, chat)\n- **Output**: Mock context object with reply methods\n- **Acceptance**: Compatible with command handlers, supports document upload\n- **Complexity**: Medium\n\n### T-121: Create E2E test: start → status → stop main chain\n- **Goal**: Verify primary user flow works end-to-end\n- **Input**: Mock runner with state transitions\n- **Output**: Test file with passing assertions\n- **Acceptance**: Tests idle→running→stopped→idle cycle, validates responses\n- **Complexity**: High\n\n### T-134: Add version management tests: upload, list, switch\n- **Goal**: Verify plan file version operations\n- **Input**: Temp directory, sample plan files\n- **Output**: Test cases for upload, list, switch operations\n- **Acceptance**: Covers success and failure paths, isolates file system\n- **Complexity**: Medium\n\n### T-141: Enhance permission tests: admin/operator/viewer boundaries\n- **Goal**: Verify permission level enforcement\n- **Input**: Mock users with different permission levels\n- **Output**: Test cases for each level\n- **Acceptance**: Tests command access per level, verifies rejection messages\n- **Complexity**: Medium\n\n---\n\n## Parallelization Guide\n\n**Can run in parallel** (marked with [P]):\n- T-001, T-002, T-003, T-004 (fixtures setup)\n- T-006, T-007 (mock helpers)\n- T-101 ~ T-104 (US-1 tests)\n- T-111 ~ T-114 (US-2 tests)\n- T-131 ~ T-133 (US-4 validation tests)\n- T-141 ~ T-146 (US-5 permission tests)\n\n**Must run sequentially**:\n- T-005 depends on T-001 ~ T-004\n- T-121 ~ T-124 (E2E tests need mock runner ready)\n- T-137 (integration test needs other tests stable)\n- T-901 ~ T-903 (polish phase)\n","file_path":"/Users/loneyu/SelfProjects/PrizmClaw/.prizmkit/specs/007-test-and-validation-suite/tasks.md"}}],"model":"glm-5.0","role":"assistant","stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":40977,"output_tokens":2296,"cache_creation_input_tokens":null,"cache_read_input_tokens":null,"cache_creation":null,"server_tool_use":null,"service_tier":null}},"parent_tool_use_id":"019cdeaf93760837ebd601924e6d630f","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T20:58:59.951Z","_requestId":"f8b0d56a051a42089a34cee3b1b65359"}
