md Test Matrix |\n| **helpers directory structure** — plan.md shows `tests/helpers/` but no T-001~T-009 creates this directory | MEDIUM | plan.md:28-31 vs tasks.md:5-13 |\n\n---\n\n### 4. Prizm Rules Alignment\n\n| Finding | Level | Location |\n|---------|-------|----------|\n| Dependencies F-003/F-004/F-005/F-006 verified — all services exist in src/services/ and src/security/ | ✅ PASS | spec.md:7 |\n| Language alignment verified — JavaScript (ESM) with Node.js test runner (D1) | ✅ PASS | spec.md:133 |\n\n---\n\n### 5. Coverage Gap Detection\n\n**User Story → Task Mapping:**\n\n| User Story | AC | Tasks | Coverage |\n|------------|-----|-------|----------|\n| US-1 | AC-1.1~1.4 | T-101~104 | ✅ Complete |\n| US-2 | AC-2.1~2.4 | T-111~114 | ✅ Complete |\n| US-3 | AC-3.1~3.4 | T-121~124 | ✅ Complete |\n| US-4 | AC-4.1~4.4 | T-131~137 | ✅ Complete |\n| US-5 | AC-5.1~5.4 | T-141~149 | ✅ Complete |\n\n**Test Matrix → Task Mapping:**\n\n| Test Matrix File | Priority | Task | Gap |\n|------------------|----------|------|-----|\n| parser.test.js | High | T-101 | ✅ |\n| registry.test.js | High | T-102 | ✅ |\n| validator.test.js | High | T-103 | ✅ |\n| formatter.test.js | Medium | T-104 | ✅ |\n| pipeline-controller.test.js | High | T-112 | ✅ |\n| plan-ingestion-service.test.js | High | T-113 | ✅ |\n| **status-aggregator.test.js** | **High** | **❌ NONE** | **MISSING** |\n| permission-guard.test.js | High | T-141~143 | ✅ |\n| param-sanitizer.test.js | High | T-144~146 | ✅ |\n| confirmation-manager.test.js | Medium | T-147~148 | ✅ |\n| e2e-main-chain.test.js | Critical | T-121~124 | ✅ |\n| security-flow.test.js | High | T-149 | ✅ |\n| plan-version-flow.test.js | High | T-137 | ✅ |\n\n**NFR Coverage:**\n\n| NFR | Requirement | Task | Gap |\n|-----|-------------|------|-----|\n| NFR-1 | Unit tests < 10s | T-902 (verify) | ⚠️ Implicit |\n| NFR-1 | Integration tests < 60s | T-902 (verify) | ⚠️ Implicit |\n| NFR-2 | >80% line coverage | ❌ NO TASK | **MISSING** |\n| NFR-3 | Test data c