: tests/bot/commands/validator.test.js\n  33→- [ ] [T-104] [P] [US-1] Enhance formatter tests: output scenarios — file: tests/bot/commands/formatter.test.js\n  34→\n  35→### US-2: Control Layer Return Tests\n  36→\n  37→- [ ] [T-111] [P] [US-2] Enhance pipeline-control-service tests: all return structures — file: tests/services/pipeline-control-service.test.js\n  38→- [ ] [T-112] [P] [US-2] Enhance pipeline-controller tests: concurrency & state — file: tests/services/pipeline-controller.test.js\n  39→- [ ] [T-113] [P] [US-2] Enhance plan-ingestion-service tests: validation logic — file: tests/services/plan-ingestion-service.test.js\n  40→- [ ] [T-114] [P] [US-2] Add error path tests for control layer — file: tests/services/error-paths.test.js\n  41→\n  42→### US-3: E2E Integration Test\n  43→\n  44→- [ ] [T-121] [US-3] Create E2E test: start → status → stop main chain — file: tests/integration/e2e-main-chain.test.js\n  45→- [ ] [T-122] [US-3] Add E2E test: duplicate start prevention — file: tests/integration/e2e-main-chain.test.js\n  46→- [ ] [T-123] [US-3] Add E2E test: stop when not running — file: tests/integration/e2e-main-chain.test.js\n  47→- [ ] [T-124] [US-3] Add E2E test: state transitions verification — file: tests/integration/e2e-main-chain.test.js\n  48→\n  49→### US-4: Plan File Validation Tests\n  50→\n  51→- [ ] [T-131] [P] [US-4] Enhance schema validation tests: valid files — file: tests/services/plan-ingestion-service.test.js\n  52→- [ ] [T-132] [P] [US-4] Enhance schema validation tests: missing fields — file: tests/services/plan-ingestion-service.test.js\n  53→- [ ] [T-133] [P] [US-4] Enhance schema validation tests: type errors — file: tests/services/plan-ingestion-service.test.js\n  54→- [ ] [T-134] [US-4] Add version management tests: upload, list, switch — file: tests/services/plan-version.test.js\n  55→- [ ] [T-135] [US-4] Add version management tests: rollback — file: tests/services/plan-version.test.js\n  56→- [ ] [T-136] [US-4] Add version