ts/fixtures/plans/`, `tests/fixtures/states/`\n  87→- **Acceptance**: Directories exist, .gitkeep in each\n  88→- **Complexity**: Low\n  89→\n  90→### T-005: Create fixture loader helper\n  91→- **Goal**: Provide lazy-loading utility for test fixtures\n  92→- **Input**: Fixture relative path\n  93→- **Output**: File content (string or parsed JSON)\n  94→- **Acceptance**: `loadFixture()`, `loadJsonFixture()`, `getFixturePath()` exported\n  95→- **Complexity**: Low\n  96→\n  97→### T-006: Create mock runner helper\n  98→- **Goal**: Replace real shell execution with controlled responses\n  99→- **Input**: Response map configuration\n 100→- **Output**: Mock runner function compatible with pipeline-control-service\n 101→- **Acceptance**: Supports action routing, response sequencing, delay simulation\n 102→- **Complexity**: Medium\n 103→\n 104→### T-007: Create mock Telegram context helper\n 105→- **Goal**: Simulate Telegraf bot context for handler tests\n 106→- **Input**: Context overrides (message, user, chat)\n 107→- **Output**: Mock context object with reply methods\n 108→- **Acceptance**: Compatible with command handlers, supports document upload\n 109→- **Complexity**: Medium\n 110→\n 111→### T-121: Create E2E test: start → status → stop main chain\n 112→- **Goal**: Verify primary user flow works end-to-end\n 113→- **Input**: Mock runner with state transitions\n 114→- **Output**: Test file with passing assertions\n 115→- **Acceptance**: Tests idle→running→stopped→idle cycle, validates responses\n 116→- **Complexity**: High\n 117→\n 118→### T-134: Add version management tests: upload, list, switch\n 119→- **Goal**: Verify plan file version operations\n 120→- **Input**: Temp directory, sample plan files\n 121→- **Output**: Test cases for upload, list, switch operations\n 122→- **Acceptance**: Covers success and failure paths, isolates file system\n 123→- **Complexity**: Medium\n 124→\n 125→### T-141: Enhance permission tests: admin/operator/viewer boundaries\n 126→- **Goal**: Verify permission level enforcement\n 127→- **Input**: Mock users with different permission levels\n 128→- **Output**: Test cases for each level\n 129→- **Acceptance**: Tests command access per level, verifies rejection messages\n 130→- **Complexity**: Medium\n 131→\n 132→---\n 133→\n 134→## Parallelization Guide\n 135→\n 136→**Can run in parallel** (marked with [P]):\n 137→- T-001, T-002, T-003, T-004 (fixtures setup)\n 138→- T-006, T-007 (mock helpers)\n 139→- T-101 ~ T-104 (US-1 tests)\n 140→- T-111 ~ T-114 (US-2 tests)\n 141→- T-131 ~ T-133 (US-4 validation tests)\n 142→- T-141 ~ T-146 (US-5 permission tests)\n 143→\n 144→**Must run sequentially**:\n 145→- T-005 depends on T-001 ~ T-004\n 146→- T-121 ~ T-124 (E2E tests need mock runner ready)\n 147→- T-137 (integration test needs other tests stable)\n 148→- T-901 ~ T-903 (polish phase)\n 149→"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"019cdeb407ff468dd4921b8d49e24952","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T21:01:19.863Z","_requestId":"f8b0d56a051a42089a34cee3b1b65359"}
{"type":"user","uuid":"77199ebc-b6cb-438a-b675-50f0c02555a6","session_id":"9310a036-0fcf-4395-9365-74ce968ab0f4","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"call_e08430b32705429b987dc248","content":[{"type":"text","text":"   1→# F-007: Test and Validation Suite\n   2→\n   3→## Summary\n   4→\n   5→建立 Telegram 管道能力的测试体系，覆盖命令路由、计划文件接入、进程控制、状态聚合与权限校验。使用 Node.js 内置 test runner，补充单元与集成测试，确保核心流程在改动后可回归验证。\n   6→\n   7→**Dependencies**: F-003 (Plan Ingestion), F-004 (Pipeline Controller), F-005 (Status & Logs), F-006 (Safety Guard) — all completed\n   8→\n   9→---\n  10→\n  11→## User Stories\n  12→\n  13→### US-1: Command Parsing & Routing Tests\n  14→\n  15→**As a** 开发者 **I want** 命令解析与路由层有完整单元测试 **So that** 命令格式变化时可快速验证正确性\n  16→\n  17→**Acceptance Criteria:**\n  18→- AC-1.1: 覆盖命令解析器 (parser) 所有分支：正常命令、空参数、非法格式\n  19→- AC-1.2: 覆盖命令注册表 (registry) 查找与错误路径\n  20→- AC-1.3: 覆盖参数校验器 (validator) 边界条件\n  21→- AC-1.4: 覆盖响应格式化器 (formatter) 各种输出场景\n  22→\n  23→---\n  24→\n  25→### US-2: Control Layer Return Tests\n  26→\n  27→**As a** 开发者 **I want** 控制层 API 有完整测试覆盖 **So that** 返回结构与错误码变更时可防止回归\n  28→\n  29→**Acceptance Criteria:**\n  30→- AC-2.1: 覆盖 pipeline-control-service 所有方法返回结构\n  31→- AC-2.2: 覆盖 pipeline-controller (F-004) 并发锁与状态管理\n  32→- AC-2.3: 覆盖 plan-ingestion-service 校验与版本管理逻辑\n  33→- AC-2.4: 所有错误路径有对应测试用例\n  34→\n  35→---\n  36→\n  37→### US-3: E2E Integration Test\n  38→\n  39→**As a** 运维人员 **I want** 有一条端到端集成测试验证主链路 **So that** 我可以确信核心流程在部署后可用\n  40→\n  41→**Acceptance Criteria:**\n  42→- AC-3.1: 测试 start → status → stop 主链路（mock 外部依赖）\n  43→- AC-3.2: 验证状态流转正确：idle → running → stopped\n  44→- AC-3.3: 验证错误处理：重复启动、空停止等边界场景\n  45→- AC-3.4: 测试运行时间 < 30s，可加入 pre-commit hook\n  46→\n  47→---\n  48→\n  49→### US-4: Plan File Validation Tests\n  50→\n  51→**As a** 开发者 **I want** 计划文件校验与版本切换有自动化测试 **So that** 上传流程变更时可防止回归\n  52→\n  53→**Acceptance Criteria:**\n  54→- AC-4.1: 覆盖 JSON schema 校验：合法文件、缺失字段、类型错误\n  55→- AC-4.2: 覆盖版本管理：上传、列表、切换、回滚\n  56→- AC-4.3: 覆盖版本切换边界：不存在的版本、损坏的版本文件\n  57→- AC-4.4: 测试与 pipeline 集成点：动态切换计划文件路径\n  58→\n  59→---\n  60→\n  61→### US-5: Permission & Security Negative Tests\n  62→\n  63→**As a** 安全审计员 **I want** 权限与安全策略有负向测试 **So that** 未授权操作被阻断验证\n  64→\n  65→**Acceptance Criteria:**\n  66→- AC-5.1: 覆盖权限分级检查：admin/operator/viewer 各级别边界\n  67→- AC-5.2: 覆盖高风险命令拦截：stop/reset/retry/exec 权限不足场景\n  68→- AC-5.3: 覆盖参数净化：路径穿越、shell 注入、危险字符\n  69→- AC-5.4: 覆盖确认机制：超时取消、强制跳过 (--force)\n  70→\n  71→---\n  72→\n  73→## Non-Functional Requirements\n  74→\n  75→### NFR-1: Performance\n  76→- 单元测试套件运行 < 10s\n  77→- 集成测试套件运行 < 60s\n  78→- 测试可并行执行\n  79→\n  80→### NFR-2: Coverage\n  81→- 核心模块行覆盖率 > 80%\n  82→- 关键路径 (happy path) 100% 覆盖\n  83→- 错误路径 > 70% 覆盖\n  84→\n  85→### NFR-3: Maintainability\n  86→- 测试文件与源文件结构对应\n  87→- 使用统一的 mock/stub 策略\n  88→- 测试数据集中管理\n  89→\n  90→---\n  91→\n  92→## Scope Boundaries\n  93→\n  94→### In Scope\n  95→- 补充缺失的单元测试\n  96→- 新增集成测试覆盖主链路\n  97→- 负向测试覆盖安全策略\n  98→- 测试工具函数与 fixtures\n  99→- CI 集成（package.json scripts）\n 100→\n 101→### Out of Scope\n 102→- 性能/压力测试\n 103→- 端到端 UI 测试\n 104→- 外部服务 mock（Telegram API）改为单元测试\n 105→- 代码覆盖率报告服务集成\n 106→\n 107→---\n 108→\n 109→## Test Matrix\n 110→\n 111→| Area | Test Type | Priority | Target File |\n 112→|------|-----------|----------|-------------|\n 113→| Command Parser | Unit | High | tests/bot/commands/parser.test.js |\n 114→| Command Registry | Unit | High | tests/bot/commands/registry.test.js |\n 115→| Param Validator | Unit | High | tests/bot/commands/validator.test.js |\n 116→| Response Formatter | Unit | Medium | tests/bot/commands/formatter.test.js |\n 117→| Pipeline Controller | Unit | High | tests/services/pipeline-controller.test.js |\n 118→| Plan Ingestion | Unit | High | tests/services/plan-ingestion-service.test.js |\n 119→| Status Aggregator | Unit | High | tests/services/status-aggregator.test.js |\n 120→| Permission Guard | Unit | High | tests/security/permission-guard.test.js |\n 121→| Param Sanitizer | Unit | High | tests/security/param-sanitizer.test.js |\n 122→| Confirmation Manager | Unit | Medium | tests/security/confirmation-manager.test.js |\n 123→| E2E Main Chain | Integration | Critical | tests/integration/e2e-main-chain.test.js |\n 124→| Permission Flow | Integration | High | tests/integration/security-flow.test.js |\n 125→| Plan Version Flow | Integration | High | tests/integration/plan-version-flow.test.js |\n 126→\n 127→---\n 128→\n 129→## Decisions\n 130→\n 131→| ID | Date | Decision |\n 132→|----|------|----------|\n 133→| D1 | 2026-03-14 | 使用 Node.js 内置 test runner（与项目一致），不引入 Jest |\n 134→| D2 | 2026-03-14 | 集成测试使用 mock 替代真实 shell 脚本执行 |\n 135→| D3 | 2026-03-14 | 测试 fixtures 放置 tests/fixtures/ 目录 |\n 136→| D4 | 2026-03-14 | 不新建覆盖率工具，使用 node --test 内置能力 |\n 137→"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"019cdeb407ff468dd4921b8d49e24952","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T21:01:19.863Z","_requestId":"f8b0d56a051a42089a34cee3b1b65359"}
